        "name": "Multi-site observational registry — CPB hemolysis data collection",
        "description": "Prospective observational data collection across three clinical sites. Pump operating parameters (flow rate, rotational speed, inlet pressure) and hemolysis markers (plasma-free hemoglobin, normalized index of hemolysis) were recorded for 47 CPB patients. No experimental manipulation of pump parameters was performed; data reflect routine clinical operating conditions. Statistical summaries were used as validation reference values for CFD output comparison.",
        "startedAtTime": "2024-06-01T00:00:00Z",
        "endedAtTime": "2025-02-28T00:00:00Z"
