    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The observational registry comparison demonstrates CFD prediction accuracy within 15% of reference hemolysis values across all five COU operating points, with RH < 1.0 confirmed in all cases. Six factors appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 3. The breadth and clinical relevance of the 47-patient multi-site observational dataset, combined with rigorous mesh refinement and code verification activities, provide sufficient evidence to support regulatory submission for the Class II CPB device. Credibility assessment accepted at Medium assurance level.",
